### 43. Tenant creates electrical maintenance (verify electrical fields)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tenant/maintenance-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{tenantToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "MCB tripping",
  "description": "Main MCB keeps tripping",
