# ====================================================================
# SECURITY LOGIN — Module Access
# ====================================================================

### 75. Security accesses visitors (should work)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/visitors
Authorization: Bearer {{securityToken}}

### 76. Security cannot access financials (expect 403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/invoices
Authorization: Bearer {{securityToken}}

### 77. Security cannot access users (expect 403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{securityToken}}

### 78. Security can see visitor passes
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/visitor-passes
Authorization: Bearer {{securityToken}}

### 79. Security can access emergency contacts
GET {{baseUrl}}/security/emergency-contacts
Authorization: Bearer {{securityToken}}

### 80. Security can see business ads
GET {{baseUrl}}/tenant/business-ads
Authorization: Bearer {{securityToken}}

# ====================================================================
# EDGE CASES
# ====================================================================

### 81. GET non-existent resource (expect 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/visitors/99999999
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 82. POST with empty body (expect 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/visitors/entry
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 83. Malformed JSON (expect 400 or 422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{ bad json here

### 84. Extremely long string input (edge case)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/announcements
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA",
  "description": "Test"
}

### 85. SQL injection attempt in search (should be safe)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/visitors?search='; DROP TABLE visitors; --
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### 86. Access with expired/invalid token (expect 401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/dashboard/summary
Authorization: Bearer eyJinvalidtoken123

### 87. Health check (public, no auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

